{"tid":763500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"許仕仁 - 強積金之父老母問候區","createTime":"2018-08-01T07:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T08:30:14.000Z","uid":47359,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8aa9f6a73de24a5de2c1e77a42b8fe3dbc991c38","tid":763500,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T07:25:52.000Z","msg":"許仕仁是天主教徒，前全國政協常委，香港特別行政區前行政會議非官守成員、前政務司司長，祖籍廣東東莞。香港傳媒以暱稱「肥龍」稱之，在政府內部曾公認其為「橋王」。 他2000年6月離開政府，到強制性公積金計劃管理局擔任首位行政總監，主司<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>設計、策劃強制性公積金。他亦因此獲稱為香港的「強積金之父」。</strong></span></span> 維基百科<br />\n<br />\n[拎翻自己錢都犯法]強積金疑似違反基本法第105條<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bsNbkS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bsNbkS</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android<br />\n<br />\n訛稱永久離港　打工仔呃MPF首坐監<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140425/18700221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140425%2F18700221&d=LDTxD5OmsASDaJfIw5fsukkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=af331d0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140425%2F18700221&h=d0dd4ac6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140425/18700221</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【提早攞強積金】發假誓隨時坐監 曾經1年拘29人涉1,200萬<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180508/58168455\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180508%2F58168455&d=LDTxD5OmsASDaJfIw5fsukkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=e4daff92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180508%2F58168455&h=3cf6096a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180508/58168455</a><br />\n<br />\n訛稱永久離港呃MPF還債　29歲女周身病獲判社服<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180731/bkn-20180731123605476-0731_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180731%2Fbkn-20180731123605476-0731_00822_001.html&d=LDTxD5OmsASDaJfIw5fsukkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a57f5825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180731/bkn-20180731123605476-0731_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n兩稱「永久離港」申提早取強積金　一人作虛假陳述判服務令 (19:24)<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20160622/s00001/1466592387853\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20160622%2Fs00001%2F1466592387853&d=LDTxD5OmsASDaJfIw5fsukkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=0b242839\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20160622%2Fs00001%2F1466592387853&h=f41d9931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20160622/s00001/1466592387853</a><br />\n<br />\n僱員訛稱永久離港提取強積金刑事罪成被重罰<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200702/06/P200702060178.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F200702%2F06%2FP200702060178.htm&d=LDTxD5OmsASDaJfIw5fsukkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=1bf1b131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200702/06/P200702060178.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n發假誓領強積金平均僅罰6400<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.e123.hk/ElderlyPro/details/28375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.e123.hk%2FElderlyPro%2Fdetails%2F28375&d=LDTxD5OmsASDaJfIw5fsukkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=118fa6ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.e123.hk/ElderlyPro/details/28375</a>"},{"pid":"8c8f29cd38508222b58726f5ae641c025065fca6","tid":763500,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T07:29:18.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif